Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小铃  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:13.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,给梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在春天成为岛上居民的梅梅和河童远野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后决定住在我们家附近的水车屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 梅梅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  到田里去给我们去拿蔬菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,远野先生也一起的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那乌龟真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…都说了远野先生是河童了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才叫我了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:00:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:47.95,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,希望改正…梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你确实是新岛民梅梅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个怪异的装束是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请…把…蔬…菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等下再来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始这里就是梅梅的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不够的东西等下再去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍有点吵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事…只是感动得说不出话来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前的风餐露宿相比的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流到岛上之后一直在北边森林生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都很害羞  一直在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是老是被有两根尾巴的老虎追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里是天国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对远野先生来说也是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河童是需要水的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说不是河童是乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人很顽固呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是顽固  是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪怎么可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是龟甲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐  梅梅为何会跟远野先生一起旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…这是无论倾听还是诉说都是充满泪水的悲伤故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是纸画剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉在…哪里看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.74,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（东映的作品都会有这个标志 所以行人才说见到过）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天爸爸做了咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大介最喜欢吃咖喱了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能交到一百个朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像之前所说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了克服害羞心理开始独自旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan\fs54.545}其实远野先生以前扮成壮鰤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan}（日本对长约60cm的鰤鱼的称呼）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被某条河边小庙的和尚所封印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得它很可怜  将费力建造的封印给解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  过去记忆中的河已经不再适合河童居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去寻找清澈的河和伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以后请多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乌龟的报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,浦岛太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.39,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（御伽草子的主人公，浦岛太郎与海龟化身的美女一起去了龙宫，\N归来后因打开百宝箱而变成白发老人）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后梅梅被带到龙宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪停不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下水抓不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,锅子还有砧板再加上些盘子会更方便点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不够的东西等下去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不能一直给他们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚就还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就稍稍感觉不害羞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想自己一个人去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才戴着面具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一直都依赖行人和小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到要与人相见就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜…拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前见过面的人也许不会很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是玲的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是岛上唯一的一群木工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从掏耳勺到房屋什么都能建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修好了我和远野先生的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好道谢才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蚂…蚁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,5  6  7  8  9  10
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蚂蚁有10只
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（蟻がとお与谢谢ありがとう发音一样）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…说修房子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  我做的柜子如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很容易打开  很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似东西还是不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真高兴  第一次被这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都说我的作品没有任何用处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的锅子和盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽情拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是把需要的东西拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能用吧  大概
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么高兴  是拒绝不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅  下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅是机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下…午…好…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是熊呢  和我…聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是…拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要穿玩偶装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话能冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边可冷静不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃和企鹅很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是旗袍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前面是迷你裙  后面是长裙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这会成为岛上流行趋势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新的岛民?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嫁祸给我的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不帮忙找犯人在这里睡懒觉的到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光是想起来就火大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才真是惨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从岛外来的叫梅梅的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是行人大人的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会是怎么样的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我相比肯定是望尘莫及的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉忘了把什么重要的事情告诉绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河童
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个新来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真够惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐平时是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔看到岛外的东西会改变性格的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幼芽该趁早拔除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我和谁都没有好好的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢加油就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…真的能在生活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别太在意比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…我无论如何也想改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅被人看到会很害羞所以要变装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是新人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再做小偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,指什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概把绫音错当成麻知姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是追赶梅梅的那个人的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我同那相貌粗暴的姐姐不同  被称为岛上最端庄美丽 贤惠的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在说谁…说得这么出神入化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是绫音的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边  真失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  刚才的话听起来是个可悲的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  绫音就不想改变自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是无稽之谈  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我最喜欢自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是做了蠢事还是做了丢人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我也认为自己很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来  今天的晚饭是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 比起改正那害羞的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须要做的事情难道不是让自己喜欢上自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…要喜欢上…自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我喜欢上的自己会有什么优点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问刚见面的我  怎么可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许正如绫音所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算保持现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅也是有优点的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有敢于一人旅行的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,画画也很擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我找朋友这点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也找到你的优点了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很中意你那害羞到令人发笑的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只要喜欢上自己  对自己有信心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自然就会治好害羞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上有这种动物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和梅梅一起漂流到岛上的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乌龟?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乌龟会叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乌龟会吃黄瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  是河童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是河童远野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了河童什么是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人果然还是顽固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河…河童?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌河童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得以前绫音被河童袭击过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  远野先生请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我  请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,远野先生  请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了…别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音是悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不停下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音  梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河童所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  远野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河童的话在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我为了让绫音吓一跳的变装
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看到绫音吃惊的样子很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河童…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 全部是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就做了旗袍  想让你们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅  这是真的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边也许比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一齐打招呼的话  梅梅会吓一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅是这里的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以后不管发生什么都要开开心心地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…还有对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回礼什么的不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,800)}{\an9\fs36.364\bord5.455\4a&HFF}\N\N{\1c&HC43A2C\3c&HFFFFFF}次回　　　　　　　　{\fs18.182}\N\N{\fs36.364}「去赢得  王之宝座」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.98,0:23:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,东部的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来我们南部的森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
